{"tid":203025,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國新核彈飛行測試成功","createTime":"2017-04-16T03:36:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-17T02:38:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"57fd838d006f75d3a9b450110d4fb5a486018629","tid":203025,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T03:36:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19991613&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170416\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19991613%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170416&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CDANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=12a15953\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19991613%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170416&h=ee56884b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19991613&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170416</a><br />\n<br />\n美國新核彈飛行測試成功<br />\n<br />\n頭條&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n美軍新型核彈B61-12可調節爆炸威力。<br />\n<br />\n北韓展示新型軍備，美國當然不甘後人，宣佈成功為「B61-12」核彈進行首次飛行測試。「B61-12」是早在1960年代服役的「B61」核彈的升級延長壽命版，爆炸力可按需要調節至最低約300噸黃色炸藥，雖然是戰術型而非滅世型核彈，但高靈活性同時令科學界擔心會令當權者更欲使用，反而加大觸發核戰風險。<br />\n測試上月14日在內華達州進行，美國桑迪亞國家實驗室（Sandia National Laboratories）聲明指，一架F16戰機由內利斯空軍基地（Nellis Air Force Base）出發，成功在沙漠投擲「B61-12」並命中托諾帕測試靶場（Tonopah Test Range）一處乾湖床，揚起巨大灰塵。<br />\n桑迪亞國家實驗室聲明強調所用核彈屬惰性，並不具有核爆力，測試主要是評估其「非核功能」及戰機搭載核彈的能力，數據要花數月時間分析，而未來三年將會進行更多飛行測試，預料2020年生產出首批「B61-12」。<br />\n美聯社<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n武器專家：做騷多過真威脅<br />\n<br />\n頭條&nbsp;5小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n開發「主體武器」針對南韓<br />\n<br />\n頭條&nbsp;5小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n尋求北韓無核化華府施最大壓力<br />\n<br />\n頭條&nbsp;5小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n檢閱女兵　金正恩笑晒口<br />\n<br />\n頭條&nbsp;5小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n歌手驚打仗　開騷前走佬<br />\n<br />\n頭條&nbsp;5小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n北韓第二號人物疑失勢<br />\n<br />\n頭條&nbsp;5小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n內地旅行社暫停北韓團<br />\n<br />\n頭條&nbsp;5小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n金正恩靠嚇晒導彈北韓：美動武即爆核戰<br />\n<br />\n頭條&nbsp;5小時前"},{"pid":"752bd6a71ce2a6c874b0b82e6ff4737a9ebc82c3","tid":203025,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T03:39:04.000Z","msg":"美軍新型核彈B61-12可調節爆炸威力。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170416/large/a0204a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170416%2Flarge%2Fa0204a.gif&h=7221eed3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"03ef26414df05865239fbfe788f8113f7687165c","tid":203025,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T03:51:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"794651418caabe197ee54af4d111ca18f76208c1","tid":203025,"uid":38825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T03:55:43.000Z","msg":"正確示範！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46b25c2b60f380ca56bf0db89c348134e6c3415e","tid":203025,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T03:59:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc74b09dcfd6fbf6bd97c5f650bf07ea9da5cc85","tid":203025,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T04:00:50.000Z","msg":"真心屈機"},{"pid":"177ed1523ab05a0bbb4e04427daf598dfc5d2c20","tid":203025,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T04:02:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正確示範！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就過期，順便"},{"pid":"7d63425dd8646f4d33ff7a9368bd882fc4fb3197","tid":2